  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c5049c5e0ff317d459948ede9e91b663, type: 2}
    content: "V\u1ED1n li\u1EBFng eo h\u1EB9p ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 5 tri\u1EC7u, kinh nghi\u1EC7m
      th\xEC b\u1EB1ng 0. M\xECnh ph\u1EA3i quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh m\u1EDF b\xE1n
      c\xE1i g\xEC tr\u01B0\u1EDBc c\u1ED5ng tr\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0111\xE2y? B\xE1n
      sai m\u1ED9t ly l\xE0 \u0111i c\u1EA3 th\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n \u0103n!"
